    "description": "渡鸦之境（Ravenbound）是一款快节奏的动作游戏，它将roguelite的挑战与开放世界的选择相结合。掌握战斗技能，打造卡组，并在阿法特的神秘世界中击败背叛者。<br><br><strong>随着每一次死亡而变得更强大</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307660/extras/6c8a21c01926ec8ddb062f02447268e4.poster.avif?t=1743067382\" width=616 height=257 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307660/extras/6c8a21c01926ec8ddb062f02447268e4.webm?t=1743067382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>你是为渡鸦服务的容魂肉身，你帮助渡鸦恢复力量，以努力解救被监禁的阿法特之神。虽然每个容魂肉身一旦在战斗中倒下就会永远逝去，但它们给渡鸦带来的力量却不会消失。因此，你每次在这个动作roguelite游戏中取得进展后，都能变得更强大。<br><br><strong>灵感来自斯堪的纳维亚民间传说的奇幻世界</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307660/extras/c8e0120ea5dc3d1648be6f52cc4690d8.poster.avif?t=1743067382\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307660/extras/c8e0120ea5dc3d1648be6f52cc4690d8.webm?t=1743067382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>徒步穿越令人惊叹的阿法特岛，或变身为渡鸦在天空中翱翔。这个奇幻世界的灵感来自斯堪的纳维亚民间传说，穿越其中，你将面对高大的巨魔、无情的树妖和来势汹汹的尸鬼，还有很多传奇生物。<br><br><strong>打造卡组并击败背叛者</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307660/extras/0a7f4463fa61d4ca04a6e75648cd76fb.poster.avif?t=1743067382\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307660/extras/0a7f4463fa61d4ca04a6e75648cd76fb.webm?t=1743067382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>在穿越阿法特的旅程中，进度以卡牌和解锁的形式出现。在每个容魂肉身的身世轮回中都会解锁新卡牌，有些是偶然的，有些则是玩家选择的。随着你变得越来越强大，奖励也会越来越丰厚。但要小心，每一个奖励都会增加背叛者的仇恨，随着仇恨的增长，背叛者的爪牙也愈发凶狠。<br><br><strong>学会掌握多变且快节奏的战斗</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307660/extras/735e3e036f00e30c5dfc98d0d0af82f9.poster.avif?t=1743067382\" width=616 height=257 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1307660/extras/735e3e036f00e30c5dfc98d0d0af82f9.webm?t=1743067382\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>要学会掌握渡鸦之境（Ravenbound）的快节奏和流畅战斗，才能打败那些越来越具挑战性而且敌意满满的阿法特生物。解锁更多的卡牌就可以获得新的盔甲、武器和魔法遗物，这将扩大你的选择范围，在每个身世轮回中提供击败渡鸦敌人的新方法。",
